{"id":89,"parent_id":73,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":89,"title":"John 16","subtitle":"","short_title":"John","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 16"],[".studySummary",["i","Jesus discourses on the mission of the Holy Ghost—He tells of His death and resurrection, announces that He is the Son of God, and says that He has overcome the world."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.1","order":"03.06.016.11171"},["b","1"],"These things have I spoken unto you, that ye should not be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"offended"],"."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.2","order":"03.06.016.11172"},["b","2"],"They shall put you out of the synagogues: yea, the time cometh, that whosoever",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"killeth"],"you will think that he doeth God service."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.3","order":"03.06.016.11173"},["b","3"],"And these things will they do unto you, because they have not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"known"],"the Father, nor me."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.4","order":"03.06.016.11174"},["b","4"],"But these things have I told you, that when the time shall come, ye may remember that I told you of them. And these things I said not unto you at the beginning, because I was with you."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.5","order":"03.06.016.11175"},["b","5"],"But now I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"go"],"my way to him that sent me; and none of you asketh me, Whither goest thou?"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.6","order":"03.06.016.11176"},["b","6"],"But because I have said these things unto you, sorrow hath filled your heart."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.7","order":"03.06.016.11177"},["b","7"],"Nevertheless I tell you the truth; It is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"expedient"],"for you that I go away: for if I go not away, the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"Comforter"],"will not come unto you; but if I depart, I will send him unto you."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.8","order":"03.06.016.11178"},["b","8"],"And when he is come, he will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"reprove"],"the world of sin, and of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"righteousness"],", and of judgment:"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.9","order":"03.06.016.11179"},["b","9"],"Of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"sin"],", because they believe not on me;"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.10","order":"03.06.016.11180"},["b","10"],"Of righteousness, because I go to my Father, and ye see me no more;"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.11","order":"03.06.016.11181"},["b","11"],"Of judgment, because the prince of this world is judged."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.12","order":"03.06.016.11182"},["b","12"],"I have yet many things to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"say"],"unto you, but ye cannot",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"bear"],"them now."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.13","order":"03.06.016.11183"},["b","13"],"Howbeit when he, the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"Spirit of truth"],", is come, he will",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"guide"],"you into all",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"truth"],": for he shall not speak of himself; but whatsoever he shall hear,",["i","that"],"shall he speak: and he will",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_13d"},"shew"],"you things to come."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.14","order":"03.06.016.11184"},["b","14"],"He shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"glorify"],"me: for he shall receive of mine, and shall shew",["i","it"],"unto you."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.15","order":"03.06.016.11185"},["b","15"],"All",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"things"],"that the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"Father"],"hath are mine: therefore said I, that he shall take of mine, and shall shew",["i","it"],"unto you."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.16","order":"03.06.016.11186"},["b","16"],"A little while, and ye shall not see me: and again, a little while, and ye shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"see"],"me, because I go to the Father."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.17","order":"03.06.016.11187"},["b","17"],"Then said",["i","some"],"of his disciples among themselves, What is this that he saith unto us, A little while, and ye shall not see me: and again, a little while, and ye shall see me: and, Because I go to the Father?"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.18","order":"03.06.016.11188"},["b","18"],"They said therefore, What is this that he saith, A little while? we cannot tell what he saith."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.19","order":"03.06.016.11189"},["b","19"],"Now Jesus knew that they were desirous to ask him, and said unto them, Do ye inquire among yourselves of that I said, A little while, and ye shall not see me: and again, a little while, and ye shall see me?"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.20","order":"03.06.016.11190"},["b","20"],"Verily, verily, I say unto you, That ye shall weep and lament, but the world shall rejoice: and ye shall be sorrowful, but your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"sorrow"],"shall be turned into",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"joy"],"."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.21","order":"03.06.016.11191"},["b","21"],"A",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"woman"],"when she is in travail hath sorrow, because her hour is come: but as soon as she is delivered of the child, she remembereth no more the anguish, for joy that a man is born into the world."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.22","order":"03.06.016.11192"},["b","22"],"And ye now therefore have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"sorrow"],": but I will see you again, and your heart shall rejoice, and your",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"joy"],"no man taketh from you."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.23","order":"03.06.016.11193"},["b","23"],"And in that day ye shall ask me",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"nothing"],". Verily, verily, I say unto you, Whatsoever ye shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"ask"],"the Father in my name, he will give",["i","it"],"you."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.24","order":"03.06.016.11194"},["b","24"],"Hitherto have ye asked nothing in my name:",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"ask"],", and ye shall receive, that your joy may be full."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.25","order":"03.06.016.11195"},["b","25"],"These things have I spoken unto you in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"proverbs"],": but the time cometh, when I shall no more speak unto you in proverbs, but I shall shew you plainly of the Father."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.26","order":"03.06.016.11196"},["b","26"],"At that day ye shall ask in my name: and I say not unto you, that I will pray the Father for you:"],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.27","order":"03.06.016.11197"},["b","27"],"For the Father himself",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"loveth"],"you, because ye have loved me, and have",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_27b"},"believed"],"that I came out from God."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.28","order":"03.06.016.11198"},["b","28"],"I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"came"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_28b"},"forth"],"from the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_28c"},"Father"],", and am come into the world: again, I leave the world, and go to the Father."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.29","order":"03.06.016.11199"},["b","29"],"His disciples said unto him, Lo, now speakest thou plainly, and speakest no proverb."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.30","order":"03.06.016.11200"},["b","30"],"Now are we sure that thou",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"knowest"],"all things, and needest not that any man should ask thee: by this we believe that thou camest forth from God."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.31","order":"03.06.016.11201"},["b","31"],"Jesus answered them, Do ye now believe?"],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.32","order":"03.06.016.11202"},["b","32"],"Behold, the hour cometh, yea, is now come, that ye shall be scattered, every man to his own, and shall leave me alone: and yet I am not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_32a"},"alone"],", because the Father is with me."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.33","order":"03.06.016.11203"},["b","33"],"These things I have spoken unto you, that in me ye might have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_33a"},"peace"],". In the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_33b"},"world"],"ye shall have",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_33c"},"tribulation"],": but be of good",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_33d"},"cheer"],"; I have",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_33e"},"overcome"],"the world."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.1a","order":"03.06.016.11204"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/offense"},"TG Offense"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.2a","order":"03.06.016.11206"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/persecution"},"TG Persecution"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.3a","order":"03.06.016.11208"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/4.6"},"Moses 4:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.5a","order":"03.06.016.11210"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/5.35"},"Luke 5:35"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.7a","order":"03.06.016.11212"},["b","7a"],["span.small","GR"],"beneficial, profitable, advantageous."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.7b","order":"03.06.016.11214"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-comforter"},"TG Holy Ghost, Comforter"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.8a","order":"03.06.016.11216"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-mission-of"},"TG Holy Ghost, Mission of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reproof"},"Reproof"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.8b","order":"03.06.016.11218"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/righteousness"},"TG Righteousness"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.9a","order":"03.06.016.11220"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sin"},"TG Sin"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.12a","order":"03.06.016.11222"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/15.15"},"John 15:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/15.16.13-18"},"3 Ne. 15:16 (13–18)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.12b","order":"03.06.016.11224"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/5.11.11-12"},"Heb. 5:11 (11–12)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/17.2.2-4"},"3 Ne. 17:2 (2–4)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/50.40"},"D&C 50:40"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/78.18.17-18"},"78:18 (17–18)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.13a","order":"03.06.016.11226"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/conscience"},"TG Conscience"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.13b","order":"03.06.016.11228"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-omniscience-of"},"TG God, Omniscience of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-gifts-of"},"Holy Ghost, Gifts of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-mission-of"},"Holy Ghost, Mission of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/inspiration"},"Inspiration"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/learn"},"Learn"],"."],["div",{"id":"13c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.13c","order":"03.06.016.11230"},["b","13c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-intelligence-of"},"TG God, Intelligence of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/truth"},"Truth"],"."],["div",{"id":"13d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.13d","order":"03.06.016.11232"},["b","13d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/revelation"},"TG Revelation"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.14a","order":"03.06.016.11234"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.13"},"Acts 3:13"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-mission-of"},"TG Holy Ghost, Mission of"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.15a","order":"03.06.016.11236"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/28.10"},"3 Ne. 28:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.59"},"D&C 76:59"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.38.37-38"},"84:38 (37–38)"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.15b","order":"03.06.016.11238"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-divine-sonship"},"TG Jesus Christ, Divine Sonship"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.16a","order":"03.06.016.11240"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.21"},"D&C 35:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.8"},"38:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.20a","order":"03.06.016.11242"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/pain"},"TG Pain"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/patience"},"Patience"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.20b","order":"03.06.016.11244"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/joy"},"TG Joy"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.21a","order":"03.06.016.11246"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/marriage-motherhood"},"TG Marriage, Motherhood"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.22a","order":"03.06.016.11248"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sorrow"},"TG Sorrow"],"."],["div",{"id":"22b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.22b","order":"03.06.016.11250"},["b","22b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/joy"},"TG Joy"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.23a","order":"03.06.016.11252"},["b","23a"],["span.small","JST"],"John 16:23 …",["i","nothing but it shall be done unto you."],"Verily, verily, I say …"],["div",{"id":"23b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.23b","order":"03.06.016.11254"},["b","23b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prayer"},"TG Prayer"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.24a","order":"03.06.016.11256"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/66.9"},"D&C 66:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.25a","order":"03.06.016.11258"},["b","25a"],["span.small","GR"],"figurative discourse, similitudes."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.27a","order":"03.06.016.11260"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-love-of"},"TG God, Love of"],"."],["div",{"id":"27b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.27b","order":"03.06.016.11262"},["b","27b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/faith"},"TG Faith"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.28a","order":"03.06.016.11264"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/8.42"},"John 8:42"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/17.8"},"17:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/4.4"},"Gal. 4:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"28b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.28b","order":"03.06.016.11266"},["b","28b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/8.14"},"John 8:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"28c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.28c","order":"03.06.016.11268"},["b","28c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/man-antemortal-existence-of"},"TG Man, Antemortal Existence of"],"."],["div",{"id":"30a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.30a","order":"03.06.016.11270"},["b","30a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-omniscience-of"},"TG God, Omniscience of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-perfection-of"},"God, Perfection of"],"."],["div",{"id":"32a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.32a","order":"03.06.016.11272"},["b","32a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/8.16,29"},"John 8:16, 29"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/14.18"},"14:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"33a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.33a","order":"03.06.016.11274"},["b","33a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/peace-of-god"},"TG Peace of God"],"."],["div",{"id":"33b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.33b","order":"03.06.016.11276"},["b","33b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/earth-purpose-of"},"TG Earth, Purpose of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/world"},"World"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/worldliness"},"Worldliness"],"."],["div",{"id":"33c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.33c","order":"03.06.016.11278"},["b","33c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/affliction"},"TG Affliction"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/test"},"Test"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/tribulation"},"Tribulation"],"."],["div",{"id":"33d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.33d","order":"03.06.016.11280"},["b","33d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/happiness"},"TG Happiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"33e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/16.33e","order":"03.06.016.11282"},["b","33e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/12.11.10-12"},"Rev. 12:11 (10–12)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/50.41"},"D&C 50:41"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.107"},"76:107"],"."]]}
